機率特論(一)-學























科目資料 
<[中文科目名稱]> 機率特論(一)  
<[英文科目名稱]> Special Topics in Stochastic Processes（I）  
<[科目代碼]>   
<[班別]> 學士班  
<[修別]> 選修  
<[學分數]> 3  
<[時數]> 3  
<[一、課程目標]> Introduction to stochastic modeling.  
<[二、資源需求評估]> Preferably by an expert in probability theory.  
<[三、先修課程]> 基礎機率(或經授課教師同意) (適合三、四年級研修)   
<[四、課程綱要]> 1. Conditional probability and conditional expectaion; Expcential Distribution. Lack of memory.  2. The Poisson processes.  3. Renewal theory.  4. Discrete time Markov chain. Long run behavior. Branching processes.   
<[五、教學要求進行方式之建議]> Lectures and discussions.  
<[六、適用入學新生年度]>






















